TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,9,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Find the inverse function of \( f(x)=\frac{1}{x+$a} \).
$BR  
\(f^{-1}(x)= \) \{ ans_rule(20) \}
$BR  
EOT

$ans1 = "1/x-$a";
ANS(fun_cmp($ans1));

